text: Aleksey Baranov (born 26 May 1954) is a Soviet skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1976 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of the Soviet Union Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1976 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
